WEBVTT

00:02.400 --> 00:04.400
Bobby:
it looks
like a... Rabbit.

00:04.467 --> 00:07.000
Peggy:
oh, I guess that's
the tail, huh?

00:07.067 --> 00:08.200
Very good, honey.

00:08.267 --> 00:09.633
What else do you see?

00:09.700 --> 00:11.333
That one looks
like a pig.

00:11.400 --> 00:13.233
No, wait--
maybe it's a ham.

00:13.300 --> 00:14.933
Bobby, in your
imagination

00:15.000 --> 00:16.733
there are no
wrong answers.

00:16.800 --> 00:17.933
Look, mom, a bee.

00:18.000 --> 00:20.133
Well, yeah, I guess
that could be

00:20.200 --> 00:22.267
maybe a puffy
little wing and...

00:22.333 --> 00:25.000
oh.

00:25.067 --> 00:26.733
We even fooled a bee.

00:26.800 --> 00:28.600
Well, that's because
bees are stupid.

00:28.667 --> 00:31.000
Fool an owl... Then we'll talk.

